OL,3,CBuilder first to be convicted over
OL,4,Crioting in Rotherham
OL,6,FA self-employed builder has become the
OL,7,Ffirst person to be convicted over
OL,8,Frioting in Rotherham at the weekend.
OL,10,FJoshua Simpson, 25, admitted
OL,11,Fassaulting a police officer during the
OL,12,Fdisturbance at a hotel housing asylum
OL,13,Fseekers.
OL,15,FSheffield Magistrates Court heard how
OL,16,FSimpson, 25, was abusive to police,
OL,17,Fwho were attempting to manage hundreds
OL,18,Fof people at the Holiday Inn Express.
OL,20,FHe kicked a riot shield, forcing it
OL,21,Fback on to an officer's leg.
