OL,6,FA deputy district judge was told the
OL,7,Fincident happened as those involved in
OL,8,FSunday's disorder were dispersing and
OL,9,FSimpson, of no fixed abode, turned up
OL,10,Fby himself in the evening after seeing
OL,11,Fthe incident unfold on a video as he
OL,12,Fwas helping a friend in Worksop,
OL,13,FNottinghamshire.
OL,15,FThe defendant admitted one count of
OL,16,Fassault of an emergency worker.
