OL,6,FHe was remanded in custody by deputy
OL,7,Fdistrict judge Simon Blakebrough, who
OL,8,Fasked for a pre-sentence report to be
OL,9,Fprepared before he is sentenced on
OL,10,FAugust 27.
OL,12,FThe judge said he could not rule out
OL,13,Fsending Simpson, who said he is
OL,14,Fcurrently homeless, to prison.
OL,16,FSimpson was one of six people in court
OL,17,Fon Tuesday over the trouble, during
OL,18,Fwhich 12 officers were injured, hotel
OL,19,Fwindows were smashed and a bin was
OL,20,Fpushed against the wall and set alight.
