OL,3,CBuilder first to be convicted over
OL,4,Crioting in Rotherham
OL,6,FAnother accused, Christopher Rodgers,
OL,7,F38, of Millmoor Road, Barnsley, denied
OL,8,Fone count of violent disorder.
OL,10,FThe court heard how he is accused of
OL,11,Fbeing part of a group that were
OL,12,Fthrowing missiles at police outside
OL,13,Fthe Holiday Inn Express in Rotherham
OL,14,Fon Sunday.
OL,16,FThe group then allegedly blocked the
OL,17,Fway as a line of officers moved
OL,18,Fforward.
