OL,6,FRodgers was bitten by a police dog
OL,7,Fbefore he was arrested, the court
OL,8,Fheard.
OL,10,FRodgers, appearing in the glass-
OL,11,Ffronted dock wearing a grey T-shirt,
OL,12,Fsaid "what a laugh" as he left court.
OL,14,FHe was remanded in custody by Deputy
OL,15,FDistrict Judge Simon Blakebrough and
OL,16,Fwill appear at Sheffield Crown Court
OL,17,Fon 20 August.
OL,19,FLiam Grey, 20, will appear at the
OL,20,Fcrown court on the same day after
OL,21,Fdenying violent disorder.
